4-6. The lines contain a list of poleis where M. Aurelius Artemon held citizenship. There are five ethnics, two of which are lost, and the list ends with the word 
               βουλευτής. This method of listing ethnics is found in other contemporary inscriptions (e.g.: I.Ephesos IV 1154; IG XII, 2 (1899), No 562.1-2; MAMA VIII (1962), No 521.1-6; 
               Moretti 1968, p. 208, No 240.9-10.
